14.	Bxf6	Bxf6
15.	Rxf6	gxf6
16.	Ne4	Ne5
17.	c3	c5
18.	Nxf6	cxd4
19.	Kh1	Qc5
20.	Qf4

This line minimizes the damage, but it also assumes white makes the optimal moves, which seems like a safe assumption given the performance so far.
